title: ArtCAM 2011 Pro
description:
ArtCAM is a unique software program which enables you to create impressive, high quality three-dimensional products starting out as two-dimensional bitmap or vector based artwork. 

ArtCAM transforms ideas into finished products far more quickly than is possible using conventional methods. Even in cases where a hand-finished look is desired, ArtCAM accelerates production. 

Using ArtCAM and a machine tool or router to machine most of the job leaves you more time to concentrate on the original design and the fine details, which together help to differentiate products in today's competitive markets.


                      How to install ArtCAM 2011


1) Run ArtCAM_2011_Setup.exe 
   Please UNCHECK "Sentinel driver" - from now you DON'T need this,
   and install software.
   During installation will be installed Delcam Exchange 2011.
   Uninstall it - i'm added a newer version.

2) Run ArtCAM_2011_HotfixIE.exe and install hotfix.

3) Go to the "Crack" folder and copy ArtCAMPro.exe 
   for 32 bit - C:Program FilesArtCAM 2011Exec
   for 64 bit - C:Program FilesArtCAM 2011Exec64
   and overwrite the original files.

   Also copy Wizards.exe and overwrite original file at 
   C:Program FilesArtCAM 2011ExecWizardsExec
   for both, 32 and 64 bit versions

4) By default ArtCAM run as Jewelsmith. 
   If you need Pro version Ã¢â‚¬â€œ in properties of shortcut 
   add text at the end of string Ã¢â‚¬â€œ Ã¢â‚¬Å“ /licence=pro.iniÃ¢â‚¬ï¿½.
                                                       
   Or, copy file ArtCAMstarter.exe at same folder as ArtCAMPro.exe 
   and run ArtCAM from shortcut of ArtCAMstarter.exe .

5) Also, if you need, you can install Delcam Exchange 
   and Delcam PostProcessor. Inside folders you will find 
   the individual latest installers separately for Win 7 and Win XP. 
   (because Delcam from 2014 version does not support Win XP)
   Each version has its own crack.

  Inside "Documentation" folder you can find User Guides 
  (DEU, ENG, ESP, FRA, ITA, PTB and RUS  languages) 
  and Training Courses in english.

                                    ATTENTION!

   - You are able open ArtCAM models only from ArtCAM 8.0 or early versions.
     You are able open 3DClipArt only from ArtCAM 9.0 or early versions.
   - Sometimes ArtCAM can't open its own files, that he was save earlier.
     So - make several saves in important projects.
   - On some computers, after about 1-2 hours of work, ArtCAM is freezes.
     In this case it is necessary to restart ArtCAM.

Enjoy :)
